          </GuiSettings>
          <Properties>
            <Configuration>
              <Text>This macro replicates the basic functionality of the Tile Tool, only giving the user the option to tile on multiple fields at the same time.  

The tool was built primarily for the predictive tool set, so it was built under the assumption that the user will be tiling on numeric fields.  The fields are sorted ascending by default, and the user has the option to tile based on equal records or equal intervals.</Text>
